15:T405,This is an orthopedic accessory component - specifically an end cap for the ARMAR PFRN (Proximal Femoral Reconstruction Nail) system. The brochure description clearly indicates 'Nail cap for PFRN nail system.' The material Ti-6Al-4V (medical-grade titanium alloy) is appropriate for this application. The 12mm diameter specification aligns with typical PFRN nail dimensions. However, the '0mm length' specification is unusual for a cap component and may indicate missing data or a low-profile design. The classification as 'Orthopedic Accessories' under 'Instruments' division is appropriate since this is a small ancillary component rather than the primary implant. Brand is missing but ARMAR is clearly the system name. Review required to: (1) verify the length specification, (2) confirm whether this is a standalone product page or should be merged into the broader PFRN system page, (3) clarify manufacturer relationship with CLAVO, and (4) obtain product images or technical documentation to ensure accurate representation.7:["$","div",null,{"className":"min-h-screen bg-[#0A0A0A] text-white","children":[["$","script",null,{"type":"application/ld+json","dangerouslySetInnerHTML":{"__html":"{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org/\",\"@type\":\"Product\",\"name\":\"Nail Cap\",\"description\":\"Nail cap for PFRN nail system\",\"brand\":{\"@type\":\"Brand\",\"name\":\"Meril\"},\"category\":\"Orthopedic Accessories\",\"manufacturer\":{\"@type\":\"Organization\",\"name\":\"CLAVO\"},\"offers\":{\"@type\":\"AggregateOffer\",\"offerCount\":\"1\",\"lowPrice\":\"0\",\"priceCurrency\":\"INR\",\"availability\":\"https://schema.org/InStock\"}}"}}],["$","div",null,{"className":"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12 md:py-24","children":[["$","nav",null,{"className":"flex mb-10 text-sm text-muted-foreground","aria-label":"Breadcrumb","children":[["$","$L12",null,{"href":"/catalog","className":"hover:text-primary transition-colors","children":"Catalog"}],["$","span",null,{"className"